      "role": "user",
      "content": "Okay, that's a bit clearer, thanks. So it sounds like the risk is pretty open-ended if there isn't a specific cap mentioned. \n\nIs there anything else in that paragraph that seems particularly aggressive or \"hidden\"? I'm just worried about things that aren't immediately obvious on the surface that could come back to haunt me later.",
